update_identity Roundcube plugin 
---------------------------------------------------
    This plugin is used to update identity email id on login. This plugin is developed to update user email id in roundcube identity when user gets logged in by usin his employeeid.
    This plugin also supports update email id when user gets logged in by email,username or employee id.

Configuration
---------------------------------------------------
    Add following configuration in config/config.inc.php

    //Domain to get email id for login id
    $config['x-mithi-domain'] = 'mithi.com';

    //Used to update identities
    //Search for email in record filtered based on searchfield
    //Allowed values: username, mail, employeenumber
    $config['get_email_searchfield'] = 'employeenumber';
